Get your grandma on our Patreon.

515
00:29:41,000 --> 00:29:44,000
Don't take your grandma's credit card.

516
00:29:44,000 --> 00:29:47,000
Grandma's gonna love Flaming Kits, okay?

517
00:29:47,000 --> 00:29:49,000
Grandma's everywhere, love Flaming Kits.

518
00:29:49,000 --> 00:29:51,000
Yeah, we don't give grandmas enough credit.

519
00:29:51,000 --> 00:29:53,000
Ooh, I remember that fuck room.

